      "side": 1,
      "message": "Agree that the amount of diff in the ABI dump is rather large.\n\nI hope (and expect) it will be less in future changes.\n\n```\nwc -l  abi/x86_64/libpldm++/gcc.dump \n3806 abi/x86_64/libpldm++/gcc.dump\nwc -l  abi/x86_64/gcc.dump \n15248 abi/x86_64/gcc.dump\n```\n\nWhat is your idea to reduce the ABI surface ?",
